snippet.title: NOOL PAROTTA | Thread Parotta Recipe Cooking In Village | Lachha Paratha | Soft Layered Parotta
snippet.description:
Today, in our village, we cook a special thread parotta recipe. This parotta has different names in different places. In Karachi, it is called "Lachha Paratha." In our place, we call it "Nool Parotta." This Parotta has different layers: on the top, it's crunchy, and in the middle, it's very soft.

Parotta lovers can try it at home. The taste is very delicious!

snippet.title: Chhaila | Shreya Ghoshal x Sunidhi Chauhan | Salim Sulaiman | Shraddha Pandit | Bhoomi 2024
snippet.description:
There's only one Shreya Ghoshal and only one Sunidhi Chauhan in this era and the divas have come together to break the internet with 'Chhaila' 🔥 Get ready to dance like never before to this Salim Sulaiman song, written by Shraddha Pandit from IGI presents Bhoomi 2024, powered by Moha.

Subscribe to Salim Sulaiman Channel: http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=SalimSulaimanMusic 🔔

Lyrics:

Kuchh Toh Hua Hai
Jabse Woh Mila Hai 
Waisa Na Mila Tha 
Na Kabhi Milega 
Haaye Uss Pe Main Toh Marr Gayi

Kaise Main Bataaun
Mera Haal Kya Hai 
Uski Nazar Ne 
Kiya Woh Asar Hai
Haaye Uss Pe Mai Toh Marr Gayi

Yeh Khushfehmiyan Sahi Nahin
Woh Toh Mera Hai Tera Nahin
Lagta Hai Tumko Maalum Hi Nahin Hai

Chhaila Woh Mera Chhaila
Rom Rom Mein Hai Phaila
Kaise Kar Gaya Mujhko Paagal

Chhaila Woh Mera Chhaila
Ishq Jaise Mera Pehla, Pehla
Kaise Kar Gaya Mujhko Paagal 

Sargam

Chhaila Mera Chhaila, Always & Forever

Sargam

Chhaila Mera Chhaila, Oo..

Antra
Hum Jab Mile The Uss Ne Kaha Tha Mujhse
Tere Bina Reh Na Paayenge

Sargam

Din Raat Baatein Karta Hai Mujhse Woh Toh
Kehta Hai Chal Bhaag Jaayenge 

Aashiq Woh Mera, Dhoondle Tu Tera
Sach Hai Kya Ab Tu Yeh Jaan Le

Chhaila Woh Mera Chhaila..

Kyun Insta Pe Stalk Mujhe Karta
Emoji Se Mere DM Ko Bharta 

Kabhi Dinner Pe, Movie Pe
Arre Kyun Date Pe Le Jaane Ko Woh Marrta

Har Waqt Mujhe Call Kyun Lagaaye (Kyun?)
Mujhe Drive Pe Bulaaye, Sataye Kyun? Kyun Mere Peeche Mandaraaye
Are You Serious?
Isi Liye Toh 

Yeh Khushfehmiyan Sahi Nahin
Woh Toh Mera Hai Tera Nahin 
Lagta Hai Tumko Maalum Hi Nahin Hai

Chhaila Mera Chhaila x2
Kaise Kar Gaya (Kar Gaya) Paagal

Chhaila Mera Chhaila
Rom Rom Me Hai Phaila
Kaise Kar Gaya Hai Mujhko Paagal

Sargam

Chhaila, He Ain’t No Lover
Paagal Kar Gaya, Kar Gaya
Kya Woh Mera
Chhaila, Mera Chhaila

Na Vo Mera Lover
Na Hai Vo Chhaila Mera

Lyrics - 
Re gaam se gori yo muh dhakna padega 
Re laamba laamba ghunghat karna padega
Main padi likhi chhori nyu ghut ghut maru na
Ji laamba laamba ghunghat main to karu na

O samjho madam ji majburi gaam me ghunghat ghana jaruri
Mekeup laari su main mahanga konya Hove ya zid puri
Saasu ladegi tera susra ladega

Is ghunghat aale baane me janu gaadi fasrya thane me
Re london aali feel na leve pagal tu haryane mein
Teri laal pili aankhya te main to daru na

Oh budya ki re chalae marji khule muh te kare allergy
Ghunghat bain karade mera hath jodke kar ree arzi
Ajay hooda ki maan na te raasa chidega

Hindi Lyrics- 
रे गाम से गोरी यो मुंह ढकना  पड़ेगा 
रे लाम्बा लाम्बा  घूंघट करना पड़ेगा 
मैं पढ़ी  लिखी छोरी न्यु घुट घुट मरू ना 
जी लाम्बा लाम्बा घूंघट मैं तो करू ना

snippet.title: 1st T20I | Highlights | West Indies Tour Of Sri Lanka | 13th October 2024
snippet.description:
Sri Lanka and West Indies faced each other in the 1st T20I at the Rangiri Dambulla International Stadium. Sri Lanka batted first and posted 179 runs for the loss of 7 wickets. West Indies started the chase well, thanks to Brandon King and Evin Lewis' half-centuries. In the end, West Indies sealed a 5-wicket victory by 19.1 overs.
.
.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Kaffara Episode 87 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 14th October 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

snippet.title: Seedhe Maut - NAMUNA  / SRK
snippet.description:
Written & Performed by Seedhe Maut
Produced by Calm
Mix & Mastered by Hurricane
Animated by Manil

Lyrics
NAMUNA

Hui bando ki thoot choti leli jab lead 
Aadat hai jeet ki roz karu repeat 
Aadat rupees ki I call it cashish 
I told her make a wish poori karu jaise 
Jeez 
Hui bando ki thoot choti fati ni reel 
Bheje mene do emoji kehti its a deal
Hoti rehti bhassad hum bhi chhode koi ni kasar 
Aisi taisi kare magar hume naushu bole chill
Man I got the big guns running 
Chale meri bm khelu jaise most wanted 
Bas SM aur kon hai? Ye pen jaise comet gire panne to pe tu gone hai put the pen in Oppenheimer aise fate jaise bomb hai 
Im a weapon like the seven got em thinking ki ye kon hai gotta tell em kon hai better kon hai launde ke liye problem kon hai con aur kon hai conor kon hai asal me iconic kon hai maut aur Kon hai cheeti 
Kon hai raunak 
kon hai goated 
Kon hai

Vo bole tum hogae ho mainstream 
Hum bole “toh kya, fir bhi best hai”
Rap mera abhi bhi ghar hai
Ye saale yaha abhi bhi guest hai
Jonsi ka banra hai Mantri
Uske Muu pe mukke turant
Khaini chabari hai kamla
Aur kamal ko kamla pasand hai
Ek maali lagara hai gamla
Par andar se khud hai murjhaya
Paisa kama bhi ni paya, aur paisa uga bhi ni paya
Gana zara bhi ni gaaya
To khaana bhi ni khaaya
Premchand ki kahani bhoola par andar ki shiksha bhula hi ni paya
Tere sar pe hai SM ka baadal
Dikhta na soon ae na moon ae
Beta tu pakka namoonahai
Lawde tu pakka namoonahai

Lyrics
SRK

Kari bohot mistakes
Par Chhode nahi dost 
Yaha pe the saanp 
Right under my nose 
Jaladi gaand 
They biting my flows 
Ab bane wo hater 
Im being real right now ab bane wo ghost 
They look at my wrist 
Puche kya hai cost 
Mene kaha mehnat hai bawe ye 
paise se hatke a lot
21 floors 
Jaise final boss 
hai Lagi bahar bheed 
Jaise ander hai shahrukh khan 

Kari mistakes
Par chode ni log
Yaha pe the saanp right under my nose
Ah fuck it mai jaane ni deta hu dushman ko jaise mai jaane ni deta hu dost ko
Pehela mai fuck deta hu apne music ko doosara mai fuck deta hu apne moksh ko 
School se hi aisa hu behen pe baat hai ajati to kho  deta hu apne hosh ko
I mean, mujhe kis baat ki sharm hai
Hu chalte hai karmo pe , ek baat bol tujhe kis baat ka bhram hai 
Jo pal raha hai charno pe
Spit so clean 
Tere dost khade danng hogae
Bando ke beech hum dil ko kaatke bhi baatre ummed
Hum kal se hai behtar aur aaj bhi hai dheet
Na hi jeb se gareeb bas shakal se shareef

Ainth 
Launde rahe mujhse ainth
Leather khole mera bat
Controversies kare catch
Mic pe ni karte hai acting
Inhe hawa lage dikhe ainth

Inki sar hi khole mera bat
Balak rahe humse ainth
Baap ko dikhate ni ainth

Lera hu din ki do flighte
Ye Nashe kyu lage diwaayi se
Iss Office me rehte 2 mic m aur 10 bhai hain yaha Paisa ni laundo yaari kamaayi hai 
Lera hu din ki do flighte
Im working hain velle ye jalte sab bhai se bohot 
Tapke khoon likhu to darte iss Siyahi se 
Ho Jebe wo moti par lagte ho light weight
Hai metal gear solid shit saanpo se bacho 
Wo jaane jab SM ki baari hai bhago 
Ye industry soche ke artist hai thago 
Wo chahte tum sote raho khwaabo me maro bawe fuck that 
Lera hu din ki do flight
Dono bhai hain gucci me jab hota mera showtime 
Inse zyada log hain show pe kyuki likhu more rhymes 
Chahiye ni koi co sign me hu wo jo kare laundo ko sign

Bawe fuck that aage peeche baatein chalein meri 
mera har track hatero ki halak me 10 jaga se phatra hai
Aankho dekhi baato pe bharosa ni, mai suspect
Lapet hi na sake beta it i tu mt fek

Bheja tujhme ni
Bheja mai khuda ka
Beh ja baato me meri 
Yaha bejaan baatein ni banata
Bheji bola kar be lawde tujhe pehele bhi kaha tha
Bheti ganga me jo haath dhoye use pehele dubara hu

Mai kare jau training
Arjun’s aiming
Saare peeche ho jao stay back

Dikhe bas lakshya
Dikhe bas haq hai
Dikhe bas satya hai
Dikhe bas fax
Inhe dikhe bas hate

Dikhe bas fake
Dikhe bas jeb
Dikhe bas cap
Dikhe bas gap
Dikhe bas aib
Dikhe bas lainth
Dikhe bas ainth

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Kaffara Episode 86 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 13th October 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:

Kaffara Episode 85 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 13th October 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

snippet.title: Din Din Diwali - Diwali Anthem | Ft. @YashrajMukhateOfficial, Sarang Sathaye & @Moti-Soap | #BhaDiPa
snippet.description:
#HappyDiwali #Diwali2024 #YashrajMukhate 

BhaDiPa, Moti, Yashraj Mukhate & team Aai aani me are here to make your Diwali more special! Wishes do come true because BhaDiPa is excited to present a brand new fusion music video – Diwali Anthem 2024 to rekindle magical nostalgic memories. Do you remember those childhood Diwali mornings and the joy of a refreshing early dawn bath with scented oil, besan, ubtan and Moti soap? Let’s experience the joy of Diwali pahat, abhyangasnaan and celebrate the festival's dawn in BhaDiPa’s style. If you like this blockbuster Diwali fusion song, share it with everyone! Let’s make it loop in everyone’s Diwali playlist and go viral! Let’s celebrate the spirit of Diwali like never before! We wish you a very Happy Diwali from Bhadipa, Moti and Yashraj!
#diwalispecial #diwalistatus #deepavali 

"Utha utha Diwali aali, Moti snanachi vel zali!"Just hearing this iconic tagline brings back a wave of nostalgia! Diwali celebrations are incomplete without Moti soap. Get yours now! For more information, click here: https://rb.gy/mfktti 

Subscribe to BhaDiPa to get alerts on our new videos! शास्त्र असते ते ! 
BhaDiPa Oversize Tees, Hoodies, and Kids merch!: https://bhadipa.merchgarage.com

All under one roof! https://bhadipa.com/ for more videos and events!
https://www.facebook.com/BhaDiPa
https://www.twitter.com/BhaDiPa
https://www.instagram.com/BhaDiPa

en.description:
#HappyDiwali #Diwali2024 #YashrajMukhate 

BhaDiPa, Moti, Yashraj Mukhate & team Aai aani me are here to make your Diwali more special! Wishes do come true because BhaDiPa is excited to present a brand new fusion music video – Diwali Anthem 2024 to rekindle magical nostalgic memories. Do you remember those childhood Diwali mornings and the joy of a refreshing early dawn bath with scented oil, besan, ubtan and Moti soap? Let’s experience the joy of Diwali pahat, abhyangasnaan and celebrate the festival's dawn in BhaDiPa’s style. If you like this blockbuster Diwali fusion song, share it with everyone! Let’s make it loop in everyone’s Diwali playlist and go viral! Let’s celebrate the spirit of Diwali like never before! We wish you a very Happy Diwali from Bhadipa, Moti and Yashraj!
#diwalispecial #diwalistatus #deepavali

mr.title: दिन दिन दिवाळी - BhaDiPa Diwali Anthem | फि. यशराज मुखाटे, सारंग साठ्ये & @Moti-Soap | #BhaDiPa
mr.description:
भाडिपा, मोती, यशराज मुखाटे आणि टीम आई आणि मी सोबत ही दिवाळी धमाकेदार होणार आहे!!!! दिवाळी पहाट हा मनाच्या जवळचा आणि nostalgic विषय आहे. ह्याच आठवणी ताज्या करण्यासाठी team भाडिपा आई मी आणि यशराज मुखाटे सोबत घेऊन आलंय एक नवीन music video - दिवाळी Anthem 2024!! लहानपणीची दिवाळी पहाट, बेसन, उटणं आणि मोती साबणाने केलेलं अभ्यंगस्नान आठवतं? दिवाळीत सकाळी लवकर उठून पहिली अंघोळ करून दिवाळी पहाट साजरा करण्याची मजा काही वेगळीच होती. चला हीच मजा पुन्हा अनुभवुया भाडिपा style मध्ये! हे blockbuster दिवाळी गाणं तुम्हाला आवडलं असेल तर सगळ्यांसोबत share करा, loop मध्ये चाललं पाहिजे, viral झालं पाहिजे!! भाडिपा, मोती, आई मी आणि यशराज यांच्याकडून तुम्हाला दिवाळीच्या खूप खूप शुभेच्छा!

परंपरा जपण्यासाठी मोतीच कारण मोती साबणाशिवाय दिवाळी आणि अभ्यंगस्नान अपूर्ण आहे! तुमचे मोती साबण आजच घरी घेऊन या. अधिक माहितीसाठी इथे click करा :  https://urldefense.com/v3/__https:/blinkit.com/dc/?collection_uuid=15ca5cc5-0f1b-4d7e-8937-c11975018038&utm_source=external&utm_medium=YT&utm_source=Moti__;!!MOA0!aVmcYMHIqTvyX7mBs_14GuV8h48iLlqrXQiUXFLwm6K-IeEEmqEAmPJybICOP8B3ms4w0Mchav1vpyTo6P2uviboL-o_n_Ghp5iEhg$

snippet.title: Every Navratri Ever | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys ,
Happy Navratri everyone , May this festive season brings lots of joy into your life like this video . Kaisi lagi video comments me btao 

also Guys to buy Mamaearth Thaali Hair Mask , 
Use Coupon Code : PAAYAL2024
Mamaearth Link: https://bit.ly/3NgORsz

Amazon Link: https://amzn.to/3NfBFUW

Flipkart Link: https://bit.ly/3Nj3Pys

Nykaa Link: https://bit.ly/3Nk4srw

This Video is all about every indian and navratri . what people do on 9 days of navratri . Girls prepping for dandiya nights , buying lehenga choli for the festival season from jwala heri , janpat , gujrati lane , gk market , Sarojini nagar , getting blouse stitched by tailor , buying oxidised jewellery , dressing for the garba with friends and dancing our hearts out and bearing the feet pain after dancing whole night , soaking feet in hot water and salt . Indian aunty looking for girls and lokda for kanjak day . Indian bahu fasting and competing who will do better vrat and saas challenging bahu for do falhari . Sisters fasting on Navratri to loose weight as well as to worship and bribe mata rani to help them pass exams . Indian mom fasting , worshiping durga , cooking tasty vrat ka khana like kuttu ki pakodi , kuttu ke paratha , kuttu ki puri , sabudana khichi , sabudana tikki , samak chawal , samak khichdi , samak pulao , makana kheer , or just doing falahari for the whole middle class family and telling them to fast as well with mom and avoiding pyaaz for 9 days no cooking with onion  . Chintu chinki and savitri preparing for kanjak day  , kids choosing their kajak gifts before hand , mummy cooking bhog chole puri halwa for the kanya . Hoping Kanya will like the navratri gifts . Going out during Navratri shopping bartan , lunch boxes , waterbottle , kanjak gifts for girls and then eating navratri thali . Breaking fast by mistake , overeating during navratri vrat . Bhai behen april fools mom eating onion outside without telling indian mother . Craving gol gappe , indian street food , spicy indian food , chilly potato , samosa , chole bhature , momo , patisse only during the navratri fast and much more
This video is filled with such memories and situations we all have been in. 
Relish and Relive your Childhood Memories.. You will have major nostalgia
Do share it with your friends and family especially mom .. Comment down your Fav Part,

Happy Navratri everyone , May this festive season brings lots of joy into your life like this video . Kaisi lagi video comments me btao 

also Guys to buy Mamaearth Thaali Hair Mask , 
Use Coupon Code : PAAYAL2024
Mamaearth Link: https://bit.ly/3NgORsz

Amazon Link: https://amzn.to/3NfBFUW

Flipkart Link: https://bit.ly/3Nj3Pys

Nykaa Link: https://bit.ly/3Nk4srw

This Video is all about every indian and navratri . what people do on 9 days of navratri . Girls prepping for dandiya nights , buying lehenga choli for the festival season from jwala heri , janpat , gujrati lane , gk market , Sarojini nagar , getting blouse stitched by tailor , buying oxidised jewellery , dressing for the garba with friends and dancing our hearts out and bearing the feet pain after dancing whole night , soaking feet in hot water and salt . Indian aunty looking for girls and lokda for kanjak day . Indian bahu fasting and competing who will do better vrat and saas challenging bahu for do falhari . Sisters fasting on Navratri to loose weight as well as to worship and bribe mata rani to help them pass exams . Indian mom fasting , worshiping durga , cooking tasty vrat ka khana like kuttu ki pakodi , kuttu ke paratha , kuttu ki puri , sabudana khichi , sabudana tikki , samak chawal , samak khichdi , samak pulao , makana kheer , or just doing falahari for the whole middle class family and telling them to fast as well with mom and avoiding pyaaz for 9 days no cooking with onion  . Chintu chinki and savitri preparing for kanjak day  , kids choosing their kajak gifts before hand , mummy cooking bhog chole puri halwa for the kanya . Hoping Kanya will like the navratri gifts . Going out during Navratri shopping bartan , lunch boxes , waterbottle , kanjak gifts for girls and then eating navratri thali . Breaking fast by mistake , overeating during navratri vrat . Bhai behen april fools mom eating onion outside without telling indian mother . Craving gol gappe , indian street food , spicy indian food , chilly potato , samosa , chole bhature , momo , patisse only during the navratri fast and much more
This video is filled with such memories and situations we all have been in. 
Relish and Relive your Childhood Memories.. You will have major nostalgia
Do share it with your friends and family especially mom .. Comment down your Fav Part,

snippet.title: Iyer को कैसे लगी Bhide के घर पे चोट? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Renovation
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to the Sony LIV Channel: 
https://www.youtube.com/user/sonyliv

Jethalal is stopped by Bhide and Abdul as they recognized that Jethalal is wearing two different shoes. Meanwhile, Babita calls Iyer and inquires about the availability of Plumber. What will be Jetha’s reaction when he finds the truth about his shoes? Why Babita is worried? To know, watch the full episode.


Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonyliv #comedy #comedy2024 #jethalal #jethalalcomedy 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The residents of the housing society, help each other find solutions when they face common, real-life challenges and get involved in sticky situations.

#tmkoc #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah 

Click here to watch episodes from TMKOC: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLn5vww_8o5KspctFrVJW13BE7LvAg5tEm

ଖାଲି ନାଁ ନୁହେଁ...ବଦଳିଛି ସମ୍ପର୍କ....
ଏଇ ନୂଆ ସମ୍ପର୍କର ଖେଳ କେଉଁ ନୂଆ ରଙ୍ଗ ନେଇ ଆସିବ ଆଦ୍ୟା ଓ ଅଂଶ ଜୀବନରେ ...?
ଦେଖନ୍ତୁ ସିନ୍ଦୁର ଖେଳ l
ସିଏ ଗଙ୍ଗା ପରି ପବିତ୍ର, ସ୍ନେହ ପ୍ରେମ ମମତାରେ ବାନ୍ଧି ରଖିଥିଲା ନିଜ ପରିବାର କୁ, ହେଲେ ବିଧିର ବିଧାନ ବଡ଼ ବିଚିତ୍ରମୟ, ନିଜ ଭଉଣୀର ଚକ୍ରାନ୍ତ ରେ  ଭାଙ୍ଗି ଗଲା ତା' ସୁଖର ସଂସାର...ନିଜ ସ୍ବାମୀ ଠାରୁ ସିଏ ହେଲା ଅଲଗା l ତା ଦେହରେ ଲାଗିଲା ମିଛ କଳଙ୍କର ଦାଗ, ଦୁଇଟି ପିଲାଙ୍କୁ ଜନ୍ମ ଦେଲା ସତ, ହେଲେ ଗୋଟେ ପିଲା ହଜିଗଲା କେଉଁ ଏକ ଦୁର୍ଘଟଣା ରେ l ଏ ହେଉଛି ଆମ ଆଦ୍ୟାର ଜୀବନ କାହାଣୀ,
ଅଂଶବି ହେଇଚି ଷଡ଼ଯନ୍ତ୍ରର ଶିକାର, ଆଦ୍ୟା କୁ ହରେଇ ସିଏ ଏବେ ଏକା, କେଉଁ ଏକ ଅଜଣା ସନ୍ତାନ କୁ ଆଶ୍ରୟ ଦେଇଛି ସିଏ, ଜାଣେ ନାହିଁ କିଏ ତା'ର ମା...? କଣ ତା'ର ବଂଶ ପରିଚୟ ?
ଏ ପିଲା ଦୁହିଁଙ୍କ ଭିତରେ କଣ ଅଛି ସମ୍ପର୍କ ..? ପିଲା ଦୁଇଟି କଣ କେବେ ଏକାଠି ହେଇ ପାରିବେ...? ଆଦ୍ୟା ଅଂଶଙ୍କର ପୁଣି ଥରେ ଯୋଡ଼ି ପାରିବକି ଭାଙ୍ଗି ଯାଇଥିବା ସମ୍ପର୍କ...?
ଏ ସବୁର ଉତ୍ତର ପାଇବାକୁ ଗଲେ ଦେଖୁଥାନ୍ତୁ ସିନ୍ଦୁର ଖେଳ

snippet.title: #Video | Chumma Chumma | चुम्मा चुम्मा | Khesari Lal Yadav | Shilpi Raj | Rajaram | नया भोजपुरी गाना
snippet.description:
देखि Chumma Anthem Of The Year अउरी तैयार हो जाई रवुआ सब झूमे खातिर ट्रेंडिंग स्टार खेसारी लाल यादव और आकांशा पूरी के साथ "चुम्मा चुम्मा " पे।'

Subscribe to our channel for more Bhojpuri Songs:
https://youtube.com/c/SaregamaHumBhojpuri

Credits:-

Title :- Chumma Chumma
Singer :- Khesari Lal Yadav & Shilpi Raj
Feat :- Akanksha Puri
Film Name:- Rajaram
Film Director:- Parag Patil
Song Director :- Sooraj Katoch (Zenith)
Lyrics :- Pinku Baba
Music :- Vinay Vinayak 
Choreographer :- Geeta Tamta (Zenith)
Dop- Rahul Yadav 
Editor :- Anand Kumar (Santu)
Associate Dop - Priyanshu Vats 
Focus Puller- Chandan Singh
Dance troupe :- Zenith
Dance Group :- (PK) Kamlesh 
GFX :- Suraj Vishwakarma 
DI :- Rohit Singh 
Production :- Amit Singh
All Costume:- Reema (Zai fashion )
Makeup Hair:- Vikash Kumar and Aryan Rajesh

Film Credits:

Production:- Technician Film Factory 
Producers :- Parag Patil & R.R. Prince

Lyrics:-

F-  फ्लेक्सी कमरिया पे नजरें गड़ाते हो 
     क्या बात है जो ये डॉलर उड़ाते हो 
M- लाली देखाके ललचावत बाड़ू 
      सुतल फीलिंग के जगावत बाड़ू 
      त दे द ना एगो नमूना 
      चूमा चूमा दे द, चूमा चूमा दे द चूमा 
F- चूमा चूमा ना देम, चूमा चूमा ना देम चूमा 

                     अंतरा -1
F-  अरे इंस्टा की मै तो रानी हूँ 
      तेरे जैसे हैँ फैन लाखों में 
      क्यूँ दूँ मै तुझे चुम्मा 
      सपना देखो बस रातों में 
M- द मौका, ल मौका -2
      गारंटी बा मजा आई हो 
      नाही देबू त दुख होइ दूना 
      चूमा चूमा दे.........

     
                   अंतरा -2
F-  मेरा चुम्मा तो बड़ी महँगा है
     बोलो क्या दोगे मुझे चुम्मे का 
     अरे मेकप में बड़े खर्चे हैँ 
     रेट लाखों हैँ मुझे छूने का 
M-  द खरचा, के परचा -2
      सब डॉलर में दे दियाई हो 
      बा रइसी रानी बुझ तु उ ना 
      चूमा चूमा दे...

Heavy rain alert is issued to Chennai, Kanchipuram, Chengalpattu and Tiruvallur districts of Tamil Nadu after a low pressure is formed in Bay of Bengal. Schools and colleges are declared holiday for the next two days and IT people are asked to work from home. 

The Greater Chennai Corporation has taken many precautionary steps to avoid urban flooding. They have mobilised relief materials, sucking pumps, have set up helplines, TN Alert app has been released to give updates to the Public.

0:00 - Message from CM
1:29 - Why 4 times more rain?
2:20 - Chennai rain prediction 
3:32 - School leave announced 
5:11 - Safety precautions 
8:34 - Alerts in various parts of Tamilnadu

snippet.title: Ratan Tata 🛑 உயிர் பிரியும் முன் சொன்ன வார்த்தைகள் 😭😭😭 | Sha boo three | Rj Sha
snippet.description:
Ratan Tata, one of India's most revered business leaders and the chairman emeritus of the Tata Group, passed away at the age of 86 on October 9, 2024, after being hospitalized in Mumbai for several days due to prolonged illness. Known for his visionary leadership, he played a pivotal role in expanding the Tata Group globally, overseeing significant acquisitions such as Jaguar Land Rover and Corus Steel. Under his guidance, the company became a global powerhouse.

snippet.title: 31-year-old Ratan Tata’s closest aide Shantanu escorts his mortal remains ahead of State funeral
snippet.description:
Ratan Tata, the 86-year-old chairman emeritus of Tata Sons, one of India's largest and most prominent companies, died on October 9. Due to his age, the business tycoon was brought to Mumbai's Breach Candy Hospital for a standard checkup. However, his situation deteriorated during the past week. Business tycoons, took to X to pay tribute to Ratan Tata for his exemplary work in India’s Industrial growth.

snippet.title: 24 Hours Zomato vs Swiggy Challenge 🔥 Who Is The BEST ?
snippet.description:
In this exciting challenge on Foodie We, Aditya and Onkar go head-to-head as they put two of India's most popular food delivery apps—Zomato and Swiggy—to the ultimate test! Each of them will order food only from the restaurants recommended by the apps and see which one suggests the best dishes. Will Zomato lead Aditya to delicious hidden gems? Or will Swiggy provide Onkar with the tastiest treats in town? Join us as we compare the apps on taste, variety, delivery time, and overall experience to find out which platform reigns supreme in the food game!

भक्त को भगवान से और जिज्ञासु को ज्ञान से जोड़ने वाला एक अनोखा अनुभव। तिलक प्रस्तुत करते हैं दिव्य भूमि भारत के प्रसिद्ध धार्मिक स्थानों के अलौकिक दर्शन। दिव्य स्थलों की तीर्थ यात्रा और संपूर्ण भागवत दर्शन का आनंद। दर्शन दो भगवान! 

Watch the video song of ''Darshan Do Bhagwaan'' here - https://youtu.be/j7EQePGkak0

मेघनाद की मृत्यु से क्रोधित हो रावण स्वयं रणभूमि में उतरता है। देवतागण पैदल नंगे पाव राम देख भगवान ब्रह्मा जी के सुझाव पर इन्द्र का सारथी मातलि को दिव्य रथ के साथ राम के पास भेजते है। रावण राम को इन्द्र के रथ पर आरूढ़ देखकर परेशान हो जाता है। राम रावण के बीच भयंकर युद्ध होता है। राम बारम्बार अपने तीखे बाणों से रावण का शीश काटते हैं किन्तु हर बार उसके धड़ पर नया शीश उग आता जाता है। देवराज इन्द्र यह विचित्र स्थिति देखकर कहते हैं कि प्रभु राम रावण के वक्ष पर बाण क्यों नहीं चलाते। इसपर भगवान ब्रह्मा गूढ़ रहस्य बताते हैं कि राम कभी रावण के हृदय को लक्ष्य करके बाण नहीं चलायेंगे क्योंकि वे जानते हैं कि रावण के हृदय में सीता का वास है, सीता के हृदय में राम का वास है और राम के हृदय में पूरी सृष्टि का वास है। इस अवस्था में यदि रावण के हृदय में बाण मारा गया तो उसके साथ सीता, स्वयं राम और पूरी सृष्टि का विनाश हो जायेगा। उधर राम की निरन्तर विफलता देखकर विभीषण उनके पास पहुँचते हैं और बताते हैं कि भगवान ब्रह्मा के वरदान से रावण की नाभि में अमृत है। राम अग्निबाण का संधान कर रावण की नाभि को भेदते हैं और उसका अमृत सुखा देते हैं। सारथि मातलि कहता है कि देवताओे ने रावण के विनाश का जो समय बताया था, वह आ चुका है। अब राम ब्रह्मास्त्र का प्रयोग कर रावण का अन्त करें। राम रावण पर ब्रह्मास्त्र चलाते हैं। रावण धरती पर आ गिरता है। प्राण छोड़ते समय पहली बार वह अपने मुख से राम को श्रीराम कहकर पुकराता है। तीनों लोक राम की जय जयकार करते हैं। 

#tilak #navratri #navratri2024 #navratrikatha #katha
